            "title": "日銀升息腳步近了？官員釋出關鍵訊號",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nBip2aMB1S8YZL7oU986lA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/cc33c9b7428ecdd674602e1a3dea1225\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E9%8A%80%E5%8D%87%E6%81%AF%E8%85%B3%E6%AD%A5%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%86-%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E9%87%8B%E5%87%BA%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E8%A8%8A%E8%99%9F-130006423.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-13 21:46:47",
